'''John Dumelo''' (born February 3,  1984) is a [[Ghanaian people|Ghanaian]] [[actor]].<ref>{{cite web | url=http://newsghana.com.gh/meet-the-sleek-gentleman-in-the-movie-industry/ |title=Meet the sleek gentleman in the movie industry | website=Newsghana.com.gh |date=19 October 2015|accessdate=25 October 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.bellanaija.com/2013/10/18/ghanaian-movie-star-john-dumelo-washes-cars-for-charity-in-accra-photos-of-munachi-abii-rekana-sharon-ojong-uche-odoh-more-at-the-event/ |title=Ghanaian Movie Star John Dumelo washes Cars for Charity in Accra! | website=Bellanaija.com |date=18 October 2013|accessdate=24 April 2014}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.bellanaija.com/2013/10/07/ghanaian-actor-john-dumelo-donates-school-supplies-to-underprivileged-children-in-cameroon/ | title=John Dumelo donates School supplies to underprivileged children in Cameroon |date=7 October 2013| website=Bellanaija.com | accessdate=24 April 2014}}</ref> He was nominated for categories ''Most Promising Actor'' and ''[[Africa Movie Academy Award for Best Actor in a Supporting Role|Best Actor in a Supporting Role]]'' at the [[6th Africa Movie Academy Awards|6th]] and [[7th Africa Movie Academy Awards|7th]] [[Africa Movie Academy Awards]] respectively.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.spyghana.com/john-dumelo-biography/ | title=John Dumelo Biography |website=Spyghana.com | accessdate=24 April 2014}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://newsghana.com.gh/john-dumelo-biography/ | title=John Dumelo Biography |website=Newsghana.com.gh | accessdate=24 April 2014}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://tv3network.com/Entertainment/qi-want-a-woman-who-is-well-endowedq-john-dumelo.html |title=I want a woman who is well endowed – John Dumelo |website=Tv3network.com |accessdate=24 April 2014 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140424132410/http://tv3network.com/Entertainment/qi-want-a-woman-who-is-well-endowedq-john-dumelo.html |archivedate=24 April 2014 |df= }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.imdb.com/name/nm3847554/ | title=John Dumelo on iMDb |website=IMDb.com |accessdate=24 April 2014}}</ref> On 1 April 2014, he became the first Ghanaian citizen to hit a million likes on [[Facebook]].<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.360nobs.com/2014/04/john-dumelo-the-first-ghanaian-celebrity-to-hit-a-million-likes-on-facebook/ |title=John Dumelo becomes first Ghanaian celebrity to hit 1 million likes |website=360nobs.com | accessdate=23 April 2014}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://akpraise.com/2014/04/02/john-dumelo-becomes-first-ghanaian-actor-to-hit-1million-likes-on-facebook/ |title=John Dumelo first Ghanaian actor to hit 1million likes on facebook |website=Akpraise.com |accessdate=23 April 2014 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140424130052/http://akpraise.com/2014/04/02/john-dumelo-becomes-first-ghanaian-actor-to-hit-1million-likes-on-facebook/ |archivedate=24 April 2014 |df= }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.dailytimes.com.ng/article/john-dumelo-hits-1million-facebook-likes | title=John Dumelo hits 1 million facebook likes |website=Dailytimes.com | accessdate=23 April 2014}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=https://www.facebook.com/pages/John-Dumelo/103975906645 |title=John Dumelo Facebook account |website=Facebook.com |accessdate=24 April 2014}}</ref>

== Personal life ==
Dumelo attended Christ the King School in [[Accra]] for his basic education. He started out as a child actor in the early 90s in a movie called ''Baby Thief.''
He had his secondary education at [[Achimota School]] and further studied at the [[Kwame Nkrumah University of Science and Technology]], where he studied Civil [[Engineering]].
John Dumelo is married to Gifty Mawunya Nkornu.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.myjoyonline.com/entertainment/2018/May-12th/videophotos-jm-yvonne-nelson-nadia-buari-ramsey-nouah-others-at-john-dumelos-marriage-ceremony.php|title=Videos/Photos: Mahama, Yvonne Nelson, Ramsey Nouah, others at John Dumelo's marriage ceremony|website=Myjoyonline.com|accessdate=4 October 2018}}</ref> The couple's first child was born on 16 October 2018. He is named John Dumelo Jnr. after his father. [https://citinewsroom.com/2018/10/16/dumelo-and-wife-happily-welcome-their-first-child/]

